- Victory

46:24.640 --> 46:29.271
- Tunneling underneath the trees
- Victory

46:29.400 --> 46:32.950
- Bringing the giant to its knees
- The morning of the dragon

46:33.080 --> 46:36.517
- All the walls fell down
- Truth lit up the street

46:36.640 --> 46:38.597
Brother greeted brother

