47:27.440 --> 47:31.434
Three years of school was nice

47:31.560 --> 47:34.280
In rice fields, planting rice

47:34.400 --> 47:39.111
- (SHOUTS)
- You did good work, you see

47:39.240 --> 47:43.029
Re-educating me

47:43.160 --> 47:46.836
Who lives a lie must change or die

47:48.840 --> 47:52.880
- Three years, how quick they moved
- (SHOUTS)

47:53.000 --> 47:56.755
- Look how the world's improved
- (SHOUTS)

47:56.880 --> 48:00.954
Saigon, that queen of sin

48:01.080 --> 48:04.073
Renamed for Ho Chi Minh

48:04.200 --> 48:08.274
SOLDIERS: Who lives a lie
must change or die

48:10.320 --> 48:13.472
But men will always be men

48:13.600 --> 48:15.432
They washed out my brain

48:15.560 --> 48:17.153
I'm still what I am

48:18.160 --> 48:21.358
Deep inside, I know what I know

48:21.480 --> 48:23.199
Wherever I go

48:23.320 --> 48:25.073
I speak Uncle Ho

48:25.200 --> 48:27.715
- And think Uncle Sam
- (SOLDIER SHOUTS)

48:28.720 --> 48:32.794
- Your name is Tran Van Dinh?
- At your service

48:32.920 --> 48:36.800
- You're called the Engineer
- Yes, sir

48:36.920 --> 48:40.675
- The People's Commissar
- Am I free?

48:40.800 --> 48:43.952
Has ordered you back here

48:44.080 --> 48:48.199
SOLDIERS: Who lives a lie
must change or die

48:49.840 --> 48:51.797
We found the man that you wanted so bad

48:51.920 --> 48:53.718
And, Commissar, you were perfectly right

48:53.840 --> 48:55.911
He had been taken up north to a camp

48:56.040 --> 48:57.952
We brought him down under cover of night

48:58.120 --> 48:59.918
Once he had served the American clique

49:00.080 --> 49:01.992
Selling our sisters and daughters
for gold

49:02.120 --> 49:03.952
Notice we caught him in less than a week

49:04.080 --> 49:06.356
BOTH: When we get orders,
we do what we're told

49:06.480 --> 49:11.236
All right, all right,
that's it, that's all

49:11.360 --> 49:14.432
You've done your job, that's it

49:14.560 --> 49:21.239
You go back, I'll take over now

49:28.920 --> 49:30.070
Kim.

49:31.560 --> 49:36.555
You will find her for me

49:36.680 --> 49:41.675
Crawl from under your shell

49:41.800 --> 49:46.431
You know who her friends were

49:46.560 --> 49:51.351
Go! See what they can tell

49:51.480 --> 49:53.676
Sniff her out

49:53.840 --> 49:56.400
Or I swear

49:56.520 --> 50:03.393
You'll look forward to hell

50:03.560 --> 50:05.916
I never saw her again

50:06.040 --> 50:08.509
I am a different man

50:08.640 --> 50:12.190
- I've been enlightened since then
- (AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

50:12.360 --> 50:13.714
Yes

50:14.720 --> 50:19.511
But men must help other men

50:19.640 --> 50:23.793
And seeing it's you,
I'll work to the bone

50:23.920 --> 50:25.798
I'll give you 48 hours

50:25.920 --> 50:29.516
If you want to stay free,
don't come back here alone

50:32.040 --> 50:36.910
