51:28.720 --> 51:29.720
ALL: Ha!

52:05.480 --> 52:07.472
(AUDIENCE APPLAUDS)

52:25.160 --> 52:29.757
Last night I dreamed you held me

52:29.880 --> 52:34.318
We slept here side by side

52:36.160 --> 52:39.710
You whispered softly to me

52:39.880 --> 52:44.352
I heard you speak my name

52:44.480 --> 52:47.040
I cried

52:47.160 --> 52:51.632
Though I know it's been so many years

52:51.760 --> 52:57.040
Through the silence of my secret tears

52:57.680 --> 53:01.879
You are here still

53:03.560 --> 53:07.952
I still

53:08.120 --> 53:12.911
I still believe

53:13.080 --> 53:17.518
You will return

53:17.640 --> 53:22.317
I know you will

53:22.440 --> 53:29.677
My heart forevermore holds still

53:29.800 --> 53:34.829
Yet still

53:34.960 --> 53:39.512
I still believe

53:39.640 --> 53:47.150
I know as long as I can keep believing

53:47.280 --> 53:51.433
I'll live

53:51.560 --> 53:53.870
Love cannot die

53:54.040 --> 53:55.713
You will return

53:57.200 --> 54:00.113
You will return

54:00.240 --> 54:07.272
And I alone know why

54:10.120 --> 54:14.000
Last night I held you sleeping

54:14.120 --> 54:18.512
Again, the nightmare came

54:20.280 --> 54:24.035
I heard you cry out something

54:24.160 --> 54:31.158
A word that sounded like a name

54:31.280 --> 54:35.911
And it hurts me more than I can bear

54:36.080 --> 54:41.075
Knowing part of you, I'll never share

54:41.640 --> 54:46.590
Never know

54:46.760 --> 54:52.119
But still

54:52.240 --> 54:57.360
I still believe

54:57.520 --> 55:00.911
The time will come

55:01.040 --> 55:06.035
When nothing keeps us apart

55:06.160 --> 55:13.351
My heart forevermore holds still

55:13.480 --> 55:15.039
- Kim!
- It's all over, I'm here

55:15.160 --> 55:18.392
There is nothing to fear

55:18.520 --> 55:22.480
Chris, what's haunting you?

55:22.600 --> 55:25.798
Won't you let me inside?
There is nothing to hide

55:27.520 --> 55:33.596
What's hurting you?

55:33.720 --> 55:35.439
- For still
- I will hold you all night

55:35.600 --> 55:37.637
I will make it all right

55:37.760 --> 55:41.959
- I still believe
- You are safe with me

55:42.080 --> 55:44.276
- As long
- And I wish you could share

55:44.440 --> 55:45.999
- As I
- What you're hiding in there

55:46.120 --> 55:51.036
- Can keep believing, I'll live
- What your hell must be

55:51.200 --> 55:54.511
- I'll live, you will return
- You can sleep now

55:54.640 --> 55:56.632
- You can cry now
- And I know why

55:56.760 --> 56:01.391
- I'm your wife now for life
- I'm yours

56:01.520 --> 56:08.677
BOTH: Until we die

56:22.680 --> 56:24.672
(AUDIENCE APPLAUDS AND CHEERS)

56:35.400 --> 56:38.632
Kim? Have you seen this girl?

56:39.680 --> 56:40.680
Hey, you

56:42.520 --> 56:43.715
(LAUGHS)

56:43.840 --> 56:46.036
Coo-coo, princess, look who's here

56:46.160 --> 56:48.834
- Your resurrected Engineer
- How did you find me?

56:48.960 --> 56:51.031
Don't look surprised, I tracked you down

56:51.160 --> 56:54.597
I have the sharpest nose in town

56:54.760 --> 56:59.789
I'm here to throw a rope
before you drown

56:59.920 --> 57:04.995
For men will always be men

57:05.120 --> 57:09.399
You change the regime,
the lust doesn't stop

57:09.520 --> 57:12.991
You and I will team up again

57:13.120 --> 57:17.034
Together we'll reap
the cream of the crop

57:17.200 --> 57:19.840
Engineer, I don't want you here

57:19.960 --> 57:23.112
I gave up that life,
you must understand

57:23.240 --> 57:26.597
Just out there is a big shot
who waits like a pup

57:26.720 --> 57:29.235
To come up and eat out of your hand, Kim

57:29.360 --> 57:30.999
The good times are back

57:31.120 --> 57:34.397
Don't go on, it's too late

57:34.520 --> 57:37.479
Not too late for my star

57:38.680 --> 57:42.959
- Please let me hide in peace
- Better to screw the police

57:43.080 --> 57:46.437
Come in, Monsieur Commissar

57:55.800 --> 58:02.354
Three years I've been away

58:02.480 --> 58:09.353
I kept faith we would meet

58:09.480 --> 58:11.995
See? I found her for you

58:12.560 --> 58:14.438
You, out in the street

58:15.640 --> 58:17.359
Out! Get out

58:25.000 --> 58:29.392
I knew in time,
fate would weave a design

58:29.520 --> 58:33.833
Tying your life and mine into one

58:33.960 --> 58:36.555
Each day I'd wait

58:36.680 --> 58:38.592
Like a soldier must wait

58:38.720 --> 58:43.840
Trusting victory to come with the sun

58:43.960 --> 58:47.840
After the fight
in the still of the night

58:48.000 --> 58:52.756
I would picture my bride, bright as jade

58:52.920 --> 58:56.914
You'll be my wife,
we will build a new life

58:57.040 --> 59:02.638
And fulfill the vow our fathers made

59:02.760 --> 59:07.118
My father's vow
can't be honored this way

59:07.240 --> 59:11.792
And I pray in my heart he'll forgive

59:11.920 --> 59:15.596
What you want now
are some words I can't say

59:15.720 --> 59:19.350
If I lied to you, how could I live?

59:19.480 --> 59:23.190
Don't say any more, not a word

59:23.320 --> 59:26.119
You will change, you will learn

59:26.240 --> 59:28.436
Look at me

59:28.560 --> 59:35.797
Don't decide too soon

59:38.080 --> 59:43.519
Somewhere deep in my soul

59:45.480 --> 59:49.076
Shines the smallest of lights

59:52.000 --> 59:55.118
And no wind blows it out

59:56.920 --> 01:00:01.836
It burns steady and strong

01:00:01.960 --> 01:00:09.675
Through the darkest of nights

01:00:11.720 --> 01:00:16.954
<i>Dju vui vay</i>

01:00:19.280 --> 01:00:22.557
<i>Vju doi may</i>

01:00:25.760 --> 01:00:30.039
<i>Dju vui vay</i>

01:00:32.120 --> 01:00:37.036
<i>Vao nyay may</i>

01:00:40.720 --> 01:00:44.999
I made a promise once
with these words

01:00:45.760 --> 01:00:49.436
Which neither time nor distance
can change

01:00:49.560 --> 01:00:52.314
He will come to me still

01:00:52.440 --> 01:00:55.797
You must be mad,
your American Jack has gone for good

01:00:55.960 --> 01:00:57.758
And he'll never come back

01:00:57.920 --> 01:01:00.435
- He ran away, Kim, he left you to rot
- No

01:01:00.560 --> 01:01:02.870
I'm sure by now he already forgot

01:01:03.000 --> 01:01:06.277
Kim, come on now, princess,
get off of your cloud

01:01:06.400 --> 01:01:08.676
I'm sorry, sir, she was talking so loud

01:01:08.800 --> 01:01:11.793
The Commissar is a powerful man

01:01:11.920 --> 01:01:14.310
A girl with brains
makes a life where she can

01:01:14.480 --> 01:01:17.598
Princess, remember your place

01:01:17.720 --> 01:01:19.712
Don't make people lose face

01:01:22.240 --> 01:01:24.357
Why do you look away?

01:01:24.480 --> 01:01:28.030
I can end all this shame

01:01:28.200 --> 01:01:31.238
All you need to say is "yes"

01:01:37.760 --> 01:01:38.989
(WHISPERS) Kim

01:01:49.440 --> 01:01:54.720
- SOLDIERS: On silent feet we came
- You hear those soldiers outside?

01:01:54.840 --> 01:01:59.357
- SOLDIERS: Breathing a sheet of flame
- They'll do whatever I say

01:01:59.480 --> 01:02:02.279
SOLDIERS:
Closing in on its rightful prey

01:02:02.400 --> 01:02:04.232
I cannot change what I feel

01:02:04.360 --> 01:02:06.591
- Burning a hundred years away
- Soldiers, come!

01:02:06.720 --> 01:02:11.078
I think you will change before my eyes

01:02:12.760 --> 01:02:15.434
- (KIM SCREAMS)
- This Me-My has just been found

01:02:15.560 --> 01:02:18.519
She hid the day we closed the bars

01:02:19.320 --> 01:02:21.357
Show them that we don't forget

01:02:21.480 --> 01:02:23.631
No one betrays us without scars

01:02:25.200 --> 01:02:29.319
- You are a woman who lived without shame
- You're an infection left over from war

01:02:29.440 --> 01:02:33.195
- You have dishonored the national name
- Re-education will cure the disease

01:02:33.320 --> 01:02:37.155
- You must be shown what we do to a leech
- See how we teach an American's whore

01:02:37.280 --> 01:02:39.476
I have heard hundreds of speeches
like these

01:02:39.600 --> 01:02:41.671
Take it from me,
you don't want to hear more

01:02:41.800 --> 01:02:44.634
It's time to act, my friends

01:02:44.760 --> 01:02:46.638
It's time

01:02:46.760 --> 01:02:49.355
SOLDIERS: Her face betrays her crime

01:02:49.480 --> 01:02:51.711
She must pay

01:02:51.840 --> 01:02:55.914
- And her partner too
- (KIM SCREAMS)

01:02:56.080 --> 01:02:57.434
Stop!

01:02:58.800 --> 01:03:02.077
- Get out!
- (SOLDIERS ARGUE)

01:03:02.200 --> 01:03:04.317
I said, get out!

01:03:04.440 --> 01:03:06.352
(SOLDIERS SHOUT)

01:03:07.560 --> 01:03:09.677
Are you waiting for them to kill me?

01:03:09.800 --> 01:03:11.473
Did you not get what he said?

01:03:11.640 --> 01:03:13.632
There's a big screw loose inside you

01:03:13.760 --> 01:03:15.353
I will rip it out of your head

01:03:15.520 --> 01:03:17.671
There's a mad dog on a rampage

01:03:17.800 --> 01:03:19.757
- Just appease him, everyone wins
- No

01:03:19.880 --> 01:03:23.635
I don't give a shit if you love him,
say you do, and we leave with our skins

01:03:23.760 --> 01:03:26.320
I have a husband I love

01:03:26.440 --> 01:03:28.557
Real as the sun in the sky

01:03:28.680 --> 01:03:31.195
- I cannot live with a lie
- You stupid...

01:03:31.320 --> 01:03:33.277
Do you see now who has power?

01:03:33.400 --> 01:03:35.357
Do you still think crazy things?

01:03:35.480 --> 01:03:37.119
Chris will come to me like the phoenix

01:03:37.240 --> 01:03:39.277
And he'll take me off on his wings

01:03:39.400 --> 01:03:41.039
You're a traitor to your country

01:03:41.160 --> 01:03:43.197
If I am, then let it be

01:03:43.320 --> 01:03:45.232
ALL: I am talking of life or death now

01:03:45.360 --> 01:03:47.477
I am talking of staying free

01:03:48.320 --> 01:03:51.279
So there it is now,
I'll be moving on

01:03:51.400 --> 01:03:54.393
If you don't need me, I'd rather be gone

01:03:54.520 --> 01:03:58.196
Two kids in love
don't need strangers around

01:03:58.320 --> 01:04:00.960
- You, just get out!
- Ho Chi Minh, I won't make a sound

01:04:04.720 --> 01:04:06.154
And as for you

01:04:07.960 --> 01:04:10.077
- Come with me
- No!

01:04:15.440 --> 01:04:18.433
There is a secret

01:04:20.720 --> 01:04:24.794
That you don't know

01:04:25.880 --> 01:04:29.271
There is a force here

01:04:31.040 --> 01:04:33.794
I never show

01:04:35.600 --> 01:04:39.753
You say it's treason

01:04:39.880 --> 01:04:43.874
To keep my vow

01:04:44.000 --> 01:04:48.916
Season after season

01:04:49.040 --> 01:04:53.592
I've survived somehow

01:04:53.720 --> 01:04:58.237
If you want the reason

01:04:58.360 --> 01:05:02.593
I will show you now

01:05:04.120 --> 01:05:05.190
Tam!

01:05:12.960 --> 01:05:13.960
It's OK.

01:05:24.720 --> 01:05:27.997
Look, Thuy, this is my son

01:05:31.320 --> 01:05:35.075
He is all that I have

01:05:37.280 --> 01:05:43.390
Now you see why I must tell you "no"

01:05:48.960 --> 01:05:52.749
No one must ever see
this thing you're showing me

01:05:52.880 --> 01:05:54.633
Your bastard fouls our name

01:05:54.800 --> 01:05:58.237
My baby's not to blame
for what I've done

01:06:00.400 --> 01:06:04.076
You must decide upon
which side you're really on

01:06:04.200 --> 01:06:07.796
- You whored to have that kid
- No! That isn't what I did

01:06:07.920 --> 01:06:09.354
Don't touch my son

01:06:12.120 --> 01:06:13.839
You must see how it is

01:06:13.960 --> 01:06:15.679
When you're my wife

01:06:15.800 --> 01:06:20.113
Keeping this child of his
brands us for life

01:06:20.240 --> 01:06:22.471
No alternative, this child cannot live

01:06:22.600 --> 01:06:23.600
No!

01:06:24.280 --> 01:06:27.956
You will not touch him

01:06:28.080 --> 01:06:31.915
- Don't touch my boy
- Kim

01:06:32.040 --> 01:06:36.000
He's what I live for

01:06:36.120 --> 01:06:41.479
He's my only joy

01:06:41.640 --> 01:06:43.552
- You will not touch him
- He is my enemy

01:06:43.680 --> 01:06:45.353
It's he who turns you from me

01:06:45.520 --> 01:06:48.035
- Don't touch my boy
- Erase him from your life

01:06:48.160 --> 01:06:49.640
Even your memory

01:06:49.760 --> 01:06:51.656
- He's what I live for
- He's one drop in a flood

01:06:51.680 --> 01:06:53.876
Left here to taint our blood

01:06:54.000 --> 01:06:56.515
- He's my only joy
- Our marriage bond is sworn

01:06:56.640 --> 01:06:57.994
Forget that he was born

01:06:58.120 --> 01:06:58.951
Get back!

01:06:59.080 --> 01:07:00.912
Of course you have a gun

01:07:01.040 --> 01:07:04.192
- You will not touch my little boy
- And now you'll shoot your cousin

01:07:04.320 --> 01:07:05.117
And it's a US gun

01:07:05.240 --> 01:07:07.471
- And do not test my will
- A gun that lost the war

01:07:07.600 --> 01:07:09.353
You're the corrupted one

01:07:09.480 --> 01:07:11.320
- I'm warning you
- Go on and shoot, don't wait

01:07:11.400 --> 01:07:13.710
- For him I'll kill
- To save your bastard son

01:07:13.880 --> 01:07:16.236
You must not hesitate

01:07:16.360 --> 01:07:17.919
The earth moves where I stand

01:07:18.040 --> 01:07:19.560
- I feel the turning of a wheel
- Shoot

01:07:19.720 --> 01:07:21.393
- I feel nothing in my hand
- Shoot

01:07:21.520 --> 01:07:24.194
- Not even the chill of steel
- Shoot

01:07:24.320 --> 01:07:26.312
You will not take my child

01:07:26.440 --> 01:07:28.636
You don't know how to kill

01:07:28.760 --> 01:07:30.513
I have no other choice

01:07:30.640 --> 01:07:34.520
What I must do I will! No!

01:07:36.160 --> 01:07:42.157
SOLDIERS: This is the hour

01:07:42.280 --> 01:07:47.799
This is our land

01:07:47.920 --> 01:07:53.632
We found the power

01:07:53.760 --> 01:07:59.313
In our brother's hand

01:07:59.440 --> 01:08:04.276
And from a storm

01:08:04.400 --> 01:08:10.510
- No!
- Pierced with light

01:08:10.640 --> 01:08:16.113
Fierce and white the lightning came

01:08:16.240 --> 01:08:24.194
A brightening flame to end the night

01:08:25.240 --> 01:08:30.872
One man to heed us

01:08:31.040 --> 01:08:35.876
Each girl, each boy

01:08:36.000 --> 01:08:42.031
One voice to lead us

01:08:42.160 --> 01:08:47.633
In a song of joy

01:08:47.760 --> 01:08:53.118
This is the hour

01:08:53.240 --> 01:09:00.352
This is our land

01:09:00.479 --> 01:09:06.953
(SHOUTS ORDERS)

01:09:16.160 --> 01:09:17.354
(GRUNTS)

01:09:22.359 --> 01:09:26.194
If you want to die in bed,
follow my example

01:09:26.319 --> 01:09:27.800
(SHOUTING)

01:09:27.920 --> 01:09:31.709
When you see a cloud ahead,
it's time to show your class

01:09:33.960 --> 01:09:37.555
Hit the door
before they make a target of your ass

01:09:42.680 --> 01:09:46.071
If you want to die in bed
in times of revolution

01:09:46.240 --> 01:09:48.709
(SPEAKS VIETNAMESE)

01:09:48.840 --> 01:09:52.277
When the flag they fly is red,
let pride fill up your chest

01:09:54.880 --> 01:09:58.510
Meanwhile pack a sack
and take the first boat heading west

01:09:58.640 --> 01:10:02.156
(SHOUTING)

01:10:05.360 --> 01:10:07.238
(WHISPERS) Where's it? Where's it?
(GRUNTS)

01:10:07.360 --> 01:10:08.999
It's still here!

01:10:09.960 --> 01:10:13.351
My precious souvenirs
of all the golden years

01:10:15.680 --> 01:10:20.118
Rolex watches in steel
that look practically real

01:10:21.800 --> 01:10:24.634
I'll need a little stock
to start me in Bangkok

01:10:26.960 --> 01:10:30.954
If you want to die in bed,
forget about your karma

01:10:32.960 --> 01:10:37.193
When your life hangs by a thread,
don't cry about the fates

01:10:39.040 --> 01:10:43.717
Grab a stash of cash
and buy a strip joint in the States

01:10:43.880 --> 01:10:45.872
(CHUCKLES)

01:10:47.520 --> 01:10:51.912
Let me stop for a bit,
this was my greatest hit

01:10:53.280 --> 01:10:58.116
Miss Saigon in her crown,
I made queen of the town

01:11:00.200 --> 01:11:04.194
I got them paying more
for just another whore

01:11:06.240 --> 01:11:11.520
Here I come, USA

01:11:11.640 --> 01:11:18.399
Your next champ's on his way

01:11:19.800 --> 01:11:23.157
For men will always be men

01:11:23.280 --> 01:11:25.431
The rules are the same

01:11:25.560 --> 01:11:27.472
For kings or for clerks

01:11:27.600 --> 01:11:30.672
Give me francs or dollars or yen

01:11:30.800 --> 01:11:32.632
I'll set up a game

01:11:32.760 --> 01:11:34.991
I know how things work

01:11:35.120 --> 01:11:36.600
Why was I born of a race

01:11:36.720 --> 01:11:40.839
That thinks only of rice
and hates entrepreneurs?

01:11:40.960 --> 01:11:44.670
Me, I belong in a place
where a man sets his price

01:11:44.800 --> 01:11:47.190
And you pay and he's yours

01:11:48.760 --> 01:11:51.912
I should be American

01:11:53.320 --> 01:11:56.870
Where every promise lands

01:11:57.040 --> 01:12:01.956
And every businessman
knows where he stands

01:12:02.080 --> 01:12:05.232
First stop Bangkok, then I roam

01:12:06.520 --> 01:12:09.957
'Cross that ocean white with foam

01:12:10.840 --> 01:12:17.155
To the place that's my heart's true home

01:12:17.280 --> 01:12:20.671
- (LOUDLY) America
- (PEOPLE CHATTER)

01:12:20.800 --> 01:12:22.359
(QUIETLY) America

01:12:22.520 --> 01:12:24.512
(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

01:12:26.400 --> 01:12:30.838
If you want to die in bed
en route to your Nirvana

01:12:32.080 --> 01:12:34.640
You grab your chance and plunge ahead

01:12:34.760 --> 01:12:36.672
And go where people win

01:12:38.440 --> 01:12:39.669
Heaven's there

01:12:42.480 --> 01:12:43.960
But shit...

01:12:44.440 --> 01:12:48.514
You need a visa to get in

01:12:48.640 --> 01:12:49.640
Ah!

01:12:55.560 --> 01:12:56.994
- ENGINEER: Get out!
- (GASPS)

01:12:57.120 --> 01:12:59.555
Engineer, Thuy is dead

01:12:59.680 --> 01:13:01.911
He was going to kill my baby and I shot

01:13:02.040 --> 01:13:04.999
You did what? Who is that?

01:13:05.120 --> 01:13:07.191
You'll be followed,
get him out of here, goodbye

01:13:07.360 --> 01:13:10.637
- Fuck!
- We must leave, Tam and I

01:13:10.760 --> 01:13:13.229
We must set off for America tonight

01:13:13.800 --> 01:13:16.269
All right, just like that

01:13:16.400 --> 01:13:20.474
Tell me how
and while you're at it, tell me why

01:13:21.480 --> 01:13:23.995
I hear the voice of my soldier

01:13:24.120 --> 01:13:27.238
Telling me to bring his son

01:13:29.920 --> 01:13:34.790
You're telling me this half-breed brat
is born the son of a Marine?

01:13:36.120 --> 01:13:38.396
Let me see his Western nose

01:13:39.720 --> 01:13:43.680
This bastard is the most beautiful sight
I've ever seen

01:13:45.680 --> 01:13:47.273
A passport in my hand

01:13:47.440 --> 01:13:49.079
(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

01:13:49.200 --> 01:13:51.396
My new life can begin

01:13:52.640 --> 01:13:56.031
Your brat's American

01:13:56.200 --> 01:14:00.114
So they must let us in

01:14:01.240 --> 01:14:06.952
In the playground of mankind

01:14:09.440 --> 01:14:12.592
The movie in my mind

01:14:16.280 --> 01:14:18.636
I'm your dear brother from now on

01:14:18.760 --> 01:14:20.911
And all our family is gone

01:14:21.040 --> 01:14:24.112
Boy, kiss your brand-new Uncle Tran

01:14:25.760 --> 01:14:27.797
(AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

01:14:27.920 --> 01:14:29.798
This kid is OK

01:14:31.440 --> 01:14:33.750
He is our <i>entrée</i>

01:14:35.280 --> 01:14:39.399
To the USA

01:14:41.520 --> 01:14:44.558
With these two little diamonds
to bait my hooks

01:14:45.640 --> 01:14:49.634
I'll book us on a cruise:
"Boat people deluxe"

01:14:49.760 --> 01:14:53.356
Don't worry about sharks
out in the Mekong Bay

01:14:53.480 --> 01:14:56.439
The pirates taking us
are more scary any day

01:14:57.560 --> 01:15:00.439
You just stay here and hide,
don't show your face outside

01:15:00.560 --> 01:15:04.918
Take care of our little dear,
I will go engineer

01:15:10.120 --> 01:15:12.919
If you want to die in bed

01:15:13.040 --> 01:15:16.431
Don't care too much for country

01:15:19.600 --> 01:15:22.399
Hit the open sea instead

01:15:22.520 --> 01:15:27.231
And float there like a cork

01:15:27.360 --> 01:15:28.714
Yeah, why not?

01:15:30.160 --> 01:15:32.152
Uncle Ho

01:15:32.280 --> 01:15:35.193
- (MIMICS ELVIS) Oh-ho ho-ho-ho...
- (AUDIENCE LAUGHS)

01:15:35.320 --> 01:15:39.075
I'll have to call you from New York

01:15:39.200 --> 01:15:43.956
New York

01:15:46.120 --> 01:15:48.112
(AUDIENCE APPLAUDS AND CHEERS)

01:16:16.040 --> 01:16:20.990
You who I cradled in my arms

01:16:21.120 --> 01:16:27.390
You asking as little as you can

01:16:30.920 --> 01:16:35.995
Little snip of a little man

01:16:37.440 --> 01:16:41.514
I know I'd give my life for you

01:16:44.320 --> 01:16:48.837
You didn't ask me to be born

